OL,3,CMarine conservation group claims
OL,4,Cdamage to seabeds is a 'national
OL,5,Cscandal'
OL,7,FMarine campaigners have accused
OL,8,FScottish ministers of continuing to
OL,9,Fallow "destructive" fishing practices
OL,10,Fto be carried out in protected areas `
OL,11,Fclaiming this not only breaches
OL,12,Finternational obligations but is a
OL,13,F"national scandal".
OL,15,FThe conservation charity Open Seas
OL,16,Fmade the comments as it published its
OL,17,FOcean Witness report, a major survey
OL,18,Fof seabeds within Scotland's marine
OL,19,Fprotected areas (MPAs).
