OL,7,FOpen Seas ` which successfully took
OL,8,Fthe Scottish Government to court in
OL,9,F2023 ` said while MPAs had been
OL,10,Fbrought in "to safeguard Scotland's
OL,11,Fmost vulnerable marine ecosystems", it
OL,12,Fadded that "numerous MPAs lack
OL,13,Feffective management measures".
OL,15,FAs a result, it claimed this allowed
OL,16,F"harmful fishing practices", such as
OL,17,Fbottom trawling and scallop dredging
OL,18,Fto persist within their boundaries.
