OL,7,F"This ongoing damage not only
OL,8,Fundermines the intended conservation
OL,9,Fgoals but also threatens the very
OL,10,Fhabitats these MPAs were established
OL,11,Fto protect," the report stated.
OL,13,FOpen Seas said its surveys "uncovered
OL,14,Fclear evidence that in many cases
OL,15,Fthese so-called 'protected' areas are
OL,16,Fmerely lines on a map with little real
OL,17,Fworld impact on marine conservation".
