OL,7,FThe Open Seas research found that
OL,8,Fmarine habitats in areas such as Papa
OL,9,FWestray as well as Loch Creran in
OL,10,FArgyll and Bute and the Sound of Jura
OL,11,Fon the west of Scotland are "actively
OL,12,Fdegraded".
OL,14,FOpen Seas accused the Scottish
OL,15,FGovernment of failing to meet
OL,16,Finternational targets under the UN
OL,17,Fconvention on biological diversity and
OL,18,Fthe global biodiversity framework.
