OL,7,FThe campaigning charity also claimed
OL,8,FScottish ministers have "broken their
OL,9,Fown promises to protect the most
OL,10,Fsensitive and important" marine
OL,11,Fhabitats.
OL,13,FOpen Seas director Phil Taylor said:
OL,14,F"Scotland's marine protections are
OL,15,Ffailing by design.
OL,17,F"Despite public statements and legal
OL,18,Fcommitments, the Scottish Government
OL,19,Fis allowing destructive fishing inside
OL,20,Fsupposedly protected areas.
