OL,7,F"These failures are not only national
OL,8,Fscandals ` they breach Scotland's
OL,9,Finternational obligations to halt
OL,10,Fbiodiversity loss and restore the
OL,11,Fhealth of our seas.
OL,13,F"We have heard repeated promises to
OL,14,Fdeliver for our seas and the coastal
OL,15,Fcommunities who rely on them from
OL,16,FScottish ministers ` sadly those
OL,17,Fpromises have been broken just as
OL,18,Fregularly."
