OL,7,FMr Taylor continued: "These are not
OL,8,Fjust technical oversights ` they are
OL,9,Fpolicy choices that carry
OL,10,Fenvironmental, legal and reputational
OL,11,Frisks.
OL,13,F"Scotland likes to be seen as a leader
OL,14,Fon the environment. But, as this
OL,15,Freport shows, we are still dragging
OL,16,Four heels while the seabed is being
OL,17,Fdragged into decline. That must
OL,18,Fchange, starting now."
